# Instructions

## Manage your cluster
Click the `Start/Stop Instance` button to start your cluster. Once you receive a green
notification with "Instance has started.", the instance is ready for you and you can SSH
to it. Run the following command in a new terminal.

```bash
ssh -p {{ forwarded_port }} user@<hostname>
```
where `hostname` is the server address. Password is the same as the one you used to log
into this app.

## Secrets
Once you find a secret, submit it in the `Submit Secret` page. You will be notified
if it is valid or not. Do not forget to select the correct project.
